e-carnival","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0144","title":"Mercado de Loulé","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_market_of_loule_926778726_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_market_of_loule_926778726_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1385422,"longitude":-8.02216148},"summary":"Discover Mercado de Loul&eacute;, an incredible covered market in this traditional town's heart. ","url":"/poi/algarve/mercado-de-loule","category":"Shopping Beaches"},{"code":"","title":"Mercado Municipal Market","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/faro city/bjv_altinkum_markets_gens_0713_01_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destination guide/portugal/faro city/bjv_altinkum_markets_gens_0713_01_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.02024,"longitude":-7.928533},"summary":"An impressive building in the heart of town, the Mercado Municipal de Faro is a lovely, cool place to come for a wander and to pick up fresh, local produce and people-watch. ","url":"/poi/algarve/mercado-municipal-market","category":"Shopping Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0066","title":"Monchique Mountains","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0066_monchique_mountains_544801578_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0066_monchique_mountains_544801578_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.3111,"longitude":-8.594789},"summary":"Potter along the narrow cobbled streets enjoying a honey-soaked cake from one of the many cake shops or take in the restorative spa waters at Caldas de Monchique. ","url":"/poi/algarve/monchique-mountains","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO5050","title":"Praia de Vale do Lobo","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_vale_de_lobo_golf_courses_636247404_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_vale_de_lobo_go